OL,3,CAnalysis finds devolved tax powers
OL,4,Ccould add #4 billion for local services
OL,6,FAllowing councils to administer and
OL,7,Fretain taxes generated locally would
OL,8,Fboost funding for services by more
OL,9,Fthan #4 billion in many areas and
OL,10,F"supercharge" economic growth, a new
OL,11,Fanalysis suggests.
OL,13,FThe report argues that new fiscal
OL,14,Farrangements which enable authorities
OL,15,Fto a proportion of revenue from income
OL,16,Ftax, stamp duty and the apprenticeship
OL,17,Flevy alongside a new tourist tax could
OL,18,Fprove transformational and support the
OL,19,Fdelivery of the Government's
OL,20,Fpriorities.
