OL,3,CAnalysis finds devolved tax powers
OL,4,Ccould add #4 billion for local services
OL,6,FThe County Councils Network, which
OL,7,Fcommissioned the report, stressed the
OL,8,Fproposals do not advocate tax rises
OL,9,Fand acknowledged that a process of
OL,10,Fredistributing tax revenue would need
OL,11,Fto be established to address regional
OL,12,Fvariations in the amounts generated.
OL,14,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner
OL,15,Frecently said she wanted "more push"
OL,16,Ftowards fiscal devolution as part of
OL,17,Fthe Government's pledge to transfer
OL,18,Fcentral decision making to local areas.
