OL,3,CAnalysis finds devolved tax powers
OL,4,Ccould add #4 billion for local services
OL,6,FThe English Devolution White Paper
OL,7,Fpublished last year states that mayors
OL,8,Fcould submit proposals for new powers,
OL,9,Fsuch as fiscal devolution, which the
OL,10,Fgovernment is obliged to consider.
OL,12,FThe guidance recently published
OL,13,Falongside the the Devolution and
OL,14,FCommunity Empowerment Bill earlier
OL,15,Fthis month stipulates that new
OL,16,Fstrategic authorities can pilot
OL,17,Fdevolved powers to make it "easier to
OL,18,Fdeepen devolution over time".
