OL,3,CAnalysis finds devolved tax powers
OL,4,Ccould add #4 billion for local services
OL,6,FThe 20 CCN councils, including top
OL,7,Ftier shire authorities and unitaries,
OL,8,Fserve about 45% of the population and
OL,9,Fcontributed almost #390 billion in
OL,10,Fnational tax receipts in 2022/23, the
OL,11,Freport said.
OL,13,FThis level of county revenues amounted
OL,14,Fto 44% of the revenue total for
OL,15,FEngland of #891.3 billion, rising to
OL,16,F57% if London's contribution is not
OL,17,Ftaken into account.
OL,19,FThis includes contributions of 62% in
OL,20,Fincome tax and and 55% in VAT.
