OL,3,CAnalysis finds devolved tax powers
OL,4,Ccould add #4 billion for local services
OL,6,FThe analysis found that expenditure in
OL,7,Fcounty areas totalled #273 billion,
OL,8,Famounting to a net benefit to the
OL,9,Fexchequer of #113.6 billion a year.
OL,11,FThe report said allowing authorities
OL,12,Fto retain "better than expected"
OL,13,Fincome tax growth could raise #3.8
OL,14,Fbillion in county areas annually and
OL,15,Fwould "dramatically incentivise" local
OL,16,Fjob creation.
