OL,6,FRetaining half of stamp duty on new
OL,7,Fhomes could provide about #237 million
OL,8,Fand encourage councils to deliver more
OL,9,Fhousing, the analysis showed, while a
OL,10,Ftourist tax set at #2 a night could
OL,11,Fgenerate about #209 million in extra
OL,12,Fannual revenue.
OL,14,FIf county and unitary councils were
OL,15,Fgranted 10% of funds from the
OL,16,Fapprenticeship levy generated locally,
OL,17,Fcouncils could direct an estimated
OL,18,F#120 million a year to skills and
OL,19,Fgrowth.
