OL,6,FHe added: "There has never been a
OL,7,Fbetter time to consider empowering
OL,8,Flocal areas with fiscal devolution and
OL,9,Flet's be clear: this is not about new
OL,10,Ftaxes for local residents and
OL,11,Fbusinesses. It's about using existing
OL,12,Ftaxes more effectively, allowing local
OL,13,Fareas who understand what's needed to
OL,14,Fdrive growth to invest to that end.
OL,16,F"More pressingly, there is the shared
OL,17,Flocal and central government need to
OL,18,Fincrease growth, create jobs and build
OL,19,Fhomes alongside the urgency to invest
OL,20,Fin local economic growth services and
OL,21,Finfrastructure.
